Long ago, in the time when I was born, the Demon
King was secretly summoned.

However, despite using a significant amount of
sacrifices in the summoning ritual to come to the
surface, the king distances himself from the army.

The subordinate demons tried to stop him, but he
dismissed their interest in invading the surface.

The king has not appeared before the Fly Knights
since then.

Humans were also frightened when they heard rumors
that the king had been summoned, but there is no
sign of him advancing.

And so, as time passed, the existence of the king
was gradually forgotten.

The Demon King concealed his horns, tail, and
wings, and lived on the surface disguised as a
human.

Originally, he had no intention of invading and
was summoned because he was interested in the
surface.

And so, the king became very fond of human culture
and settled in a rural town in the Kingdom of
Greatland.

A man falls in love with the king, who had a
splendid appearance, without suspecting that he is
a demon.

The king also fell in love with the man's
sincerity and bravery, and the two of them quickly
became united.

However, the king held onto a secret that must
never be revealed - the fact that he is a demon.

The marriage life between the king and the human
was blessed with children and went smoothly.
At that time, demons attacked the town.

The king reveals his demonic form that he had been
hiding in order to protect his family and uses his
power.

The demons that invaded were not enemies of the
king, and they quickly retreated from the town.

However, the husband also becomes frightened by
that appearance and runs away.

The demon king was deeply saddened by that and
left the town alone.

However, the king cannot forget about their
beloved spouse.
The king uses a certain magic.
A magic that relinquishes all magical power.

The demon king lost his magical power and became a
human.
